  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This observational prospective study evaluates perioperative olfaction alterations,
      comprising changes in threshold value, discrimination and identification, which occur in
      spine patients. The single group is subjected to a preoperative and a postoperative
      assessment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
